####iPY and requests packages are both required for custom IPv4 and IPv6 configuration of minions



#####to install iPY on Ubuntu 22 (master)
  apt update && sudo apt install pip
  pip install IPy
  pip install requests



  #######to install iPY on Debian Bookworm (Proxmox 8) (minion)
  apt update && apt install python3
  apt install python3-ipy



#####iPY only available for Debian Bookworm through python3 package manager
